                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37814",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=david",
                        "name": "david",
                        "displayName": "David Nussio",
                        "active": false
                    },
                    "body": "I'm using Ziad's patch that solve similar case.\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultmodule.type = Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Module\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultmodule.defaults.module = \"default\"\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultmodule.defaults.controller = \"index\"\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultmodule.defaults.action = \"index\"\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.language.type = Zend_Controller_Router_Route\r\nresources.router.routes.language.route = \":language\"\r\nresources.router.routes.language.reqs.language = \"^(it|fr|en|de)$\"\r\nresources.router.routes.language.defaults.language = \"en\"\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.default.type = Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Chain\r\nresources.router.routes.default.chain = \"language, defaultmodule\"\r\n\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=david",
                        "name": "david",
                        "displayName": "David Nussio",
                        "active": false
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-19T00:17:28.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-19T00:17:28.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/38943",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=david",
                        "name": "david",
                        "displayName": "David Nussio",
                        "active": false
                    },
                    "body": "Hello, could you change the priority of this task?\r\nI have to patch every new release to do work route chain defaults value.\r\nThanks, great work.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=david",
                        "name": "david",
                        "displayName": "David Nussio",
                        "active": false
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-03T02:44:31.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-03T02:44:31.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41307",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kevinh",
                        "name": "kevinh",
                        "displayName": "Kevin Horst",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "also tested with 1.10.1\r\n\r\nresources.frontcontroller.defaultModule               = \"default\"\r\nresources.frontcontroller.controllerDirectory         = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/controllers\"\r\nresources.frontcontroller.moduleDirectory             = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/modules\"\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultRoute.type             = Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Module\"\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultRoute.abstract         = \"On\"\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultRoute.route            = \":module\"\r\nresources.router.routes.defaultRoute.defaults.module  = \"default\"\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.language.type                 = \"Zend_Controller_Router_Route\"\r\nresources.router.routes.language.route                = \":lang\"\r\nresources.router.routes.language.reqs.lang            = \"^(en|de)$\"\r\nresources.router.routes.language.defaults.lang        = \"en\"\r\n\r\nresources.router.routes.default.type                  = \"Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Chain\"\r\nresources.router.routes.default.chain                 = \"language, defaultRoute\"\r\n\r\n\r\ntest url -> request-object\r\n\r\n\/                     -> \/en\/default\/index\/index\r\n\/en                   -> \/en\/default\/index\/index\r\n\/de                   -> \/de\/default\/index\/index\r\n\/en\/admin\/index\/index -> \/en\/admin\/index\/index\r\n\/en\/index             -> \/en\/default\/index\/index\r\n\r\nworks all great. i think, this is a blocker.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kevinh",
                        "name": "kevinh",
                        "displayName": "Kevin Horst",
